Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The light of summer is the radiance of yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:05.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the tears is a chance of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even unluckiness has a limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a case with lives at stake!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:12.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:15.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, that's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.34,0:02:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was sure that Korean BBQ restaurant was on this street.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't important.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go to another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:09.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's search one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're looking again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go back home, Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's starting to look like you’ll never find it, and isn't it already 6:30?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:22.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only 6:30!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you that I'd treat you to a luxurious meal while Ran is away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:32.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You hit someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.54,0:02:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damned food!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, send an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:41.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two pedestrians have been struck by a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:44.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The place is Beika Park, in the back street.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make it quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:49.34,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tatematsu Shinzaburaou\N\h{\fs13}Company Employee(25)\h
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:49.12,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This person--where have I seen him before?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The most unlucky man in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The most unlucky man in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:58.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was on a TV program before, in a video made by his nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won the program's prize for being the most interesting submission.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My uncle, Tatematsu Shinzaburou san, is\Nprobably the most unlucky man in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:11.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he's walking, a lot of things fall from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:16.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when he avoids them, he always twists his ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow, that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:22.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he's waiting in line, they always sell out right before him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:22.41,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:33.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why am I the only one who's so unlucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:37.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now he's finally ended up involved in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.94,0:03:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:46.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That car—it'd been waiting over\Nthere to ambush him for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:52.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As soon as he showed up, they targeted him and ran him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:53.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This wasn't a mere accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:01.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a case of attempted murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:12.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The witness remembered the car's license plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:15.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, it turned out to be a stolen car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.01,0:04:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The car has yet to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:21.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, how are the victims?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:24.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their lives aren't in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are the details?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:27.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:34.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the witness, the culprit was wearing\Nsunglasses and a hat, so his face couldn't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:39.03,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Tatematsu Shinzaburou-san was heading home\Nfrom Beika Station after getting off of work....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:43.05,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,When he stopped to exchange greetings Okonogi\NKitoyaka-san, who was taking a liesurely walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:42.55,CharCard1,,0,0,0,,\hOkonogi Kiyotaka (65)\h\N\h\h\h\h\h\hWealthy Person\h\h\h\h\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:46.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the car waiting in ambush suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:54.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that car aiming for Tatematsu-kun or Okonogi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.72,0:04:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't know, since it sped towards\Nthem exactly when the two met.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:03.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the culprit was aiming at both of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if the culprit wanted to kill both of them, he'd\Nlikely try to do so separately, one after the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means he was really just targeting one of the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:22.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if that's the case, why did the culprit\Nact exactly at such an odd moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:25.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should ask the victims if they recall\Nanyone having a grudge against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:36.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:40.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should be able to speak to Tatematsu-san soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Okonogi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:44.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is Uncle safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:49.25,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,He's Okonogi-san nephew, Sakaki Kazuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:49.23,CharCard2,,0,0,0,,\h\hSakaki Kazuma (27)\h\h\N\h\h\hOkonagi's Nephew\h\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:51.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His nephew, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an1}\h\h\h\h\h\hAnd his fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:57.49,CharCard3,,0,0,0,,\hIchikura Tomomi (25)\h\N\h\h\hKazuma's Fiancée\h\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an1}\h\h\h\h\h\hI'm Ichikura Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an1}When I heard about the accident from\N\h\h\h\hKazuma-san, I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:06:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His life isn't in any danger, but it may take\Nsome time before he regains consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did it have to happen to Okonogi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.17,0:06:10.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of person would do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.46,0:06:13.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something's bugging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okonogi-san is quite wealthy, but he has no family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.47,0:06:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His nephew is his only blood relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:24.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:30.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Okonogi-san were to die, all of his\Nbelongings would become his nephew’s.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:30.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:34.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that this guy has a huge debt to Okonogi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:41.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This evening at around 6:30, when Okonogi-san was hit by a car...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:43.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where were you, Sakaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:46.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you suspecting me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:47.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.79,0:06:54.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the culprit was aiming at the other guy who was there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:56.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okonogi-san ended up involved against his will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:07:04.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, the police must check the alibis\Nof all close family members for both victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:08.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakaki-san, Ichikura-san, please cooperate with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:13.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ichikura-san, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:21.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's just that I heard he was going to the\Nfarewell party for a senior in his company.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:23.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I felt sick, so I left the office at noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I then went to sleep in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:32.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I live alone, so I have no witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you, Ichikura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was loitering around near the Touto\NDepartment Store in Ginza from about 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it was exactly 6:00 when I decided\Nthat it was time to head back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you with anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:52.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:54.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was also alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for someone who can prove it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:08:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, at that time, there was some commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.99,0:08:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Commotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I sent a message to Kazuma-san about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bomb case?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:20.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Okumura, did you know about this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'll go confirm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, what, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mouri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:30.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I just arrived at the Touto Department Store, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:35.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"A timed bomb has been discovered in\Nthe women restroom on the 5th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:36.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Scary."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:37.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:38.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A suspicious object had been found in the restroom at about 6:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:48.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of the guests and employees were\Nevacuated, so there was a lot of commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it turned out to be a bad prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:55.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bombs were completely fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:56.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.96,0:08:59.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, the bombs were not found in\Nthe women's restroom on the 5th floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But rather in the men's on the 6th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:12.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To make a mistake when giving information while\Na commotion is going on happens quite often.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:16.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And whether it was on the 5th floor or the 6th floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or if the bombs were real or fake,\Nthis has no connection to our case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Given that it's true the bombs caused some commotion at 6:30...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You being able to communicate that correlating\Ninformation at 6:40 proves you were there at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:37.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you drove at high speeds, it would take at least an\Nhour to go from the Touto Department Store to Beika district.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:43.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The commotion caused by those fake bombs just\Nso happened to give you an alibi, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:45.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe this lady is lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Sakaki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems you owe Okonogi-san quite a large amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:57.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're police officers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatematsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That car...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That car tried to kill me in order to silence me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silence you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My payday was the day before yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:20.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought about getting some luxury food, as I do once in a while, and\Nbought some expensive meat and sashimi at the nearby supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But as soon as I left...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:24.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone snatched it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:29.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when I started to run after the thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was really terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really are an unlucky guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd seen your face somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the guy who was on TV, and is said\Nto be the most unlucky guy in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:52.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess everybody watched that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:55.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that isn't the end of the story yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That night, I got a call from the snatcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How dare you inform the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen my face, I cannot allow you to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll seal your mouth for all of eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A murder declaration?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And today, just as he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:19.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, to kill someone just to silence them over snatching\Nsome groceries is going a bit overboard, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:21.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:23.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was the same guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:30.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:33.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The theft and attempted murder to silence him are linked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:36.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go check on the old man's condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But is this case really that simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Tatematsu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you an acquaintance of that old man, Okonogi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:56.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know his name, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:12:00.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd met at that place every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I always come back on the same train, and he\Nalso goes for leisurely walks at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please tell us further details regarding the snatching\Nincident that happened the day before yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:12.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the call you received the same evening, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, we're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We know who the culprit is, so the rest is just police work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:23.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:25.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something just isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:31.40,StpTitle01,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}The Next Morning
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:32.53,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What concerns me the most is the\Ntiming of when the car sped forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:38.16,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,If it was an attempt on Tatematsu-san's life, he\Nwould've been targeted when he was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:39.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did it have to be then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're already here this early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A brat shouldn't stick his nose into things uncessarily, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take a look at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:13:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that "most unlucky guy in Japan" is quite depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:06.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's thinking, "Okonogi-san has nothing to do\Nwith it, and only got involved because of me."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:09.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured I'd go cheer him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even Uncle has some good ideas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:13.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a lotta good ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:18.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe, on the contrary...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.89,0:13:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the culprit resorted to snatching in order to hide something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:27.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it all makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:31.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if that's the case, the person who\Nsaw the culprit has to be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:41.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone following Tatematsu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think it happened here a few days ago, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:49.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:51.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It may have something to do with Tatematsu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A strange guy came.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that guy short and a little bit overweight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:14:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it was some beautiful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:01.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:07.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first, I thought it was his girlfriend, but\NTatematsu-san isn't that kind of guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:14.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The discovery of the suspicious package was not unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 6:30, an anonymous call was made\Nto the Touto Department Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:20.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said they set up time bombs in the restrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the women's restroom on the 5th floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:25.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We haven't made it public because it's a secret investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it seems a boy who came to shop moved\Nthem to the men's restroom on the 6th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the while being unaware they were fake bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how it happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything fits with my deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:47.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're that boy from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's Okonogi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:54.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't know when he will regain consciousness,\Nso I figured I'd get some lunch in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:58.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, only Okonogi-san and Ichikura-san\Nare in the hospital room now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:02.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I completely solved the mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's why we hurried over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:16.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we rushed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:22.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don’t remember that, but maybe I'm schizophrenic...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've brought him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.10,0:15:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's exactly as you said, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you something too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:31.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.38,0:15:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:15:58.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What were you about to do, Tomomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:00.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this, Mouri-san!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you keep asking, I can't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May...be.. my schizo... phre... ny...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did it come?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ichikura-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though you rushed to hide that\Nwet towel, your act has come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, you failed to kill him, even though\Nyou tired to disguise it as a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Ichikura-san has an alibi for the incident yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:41.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who drove into us yesterday\Nwas the culprit who stole my groceries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of that was part of Ichikura-san's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:52.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First of all, the culprit was targeting Okonogi-san in this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatematsu-san, you were used by the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.40,0:17:01.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was used?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:05.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ichikura-san intended to kill Okonogi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But with a simple murder, she knew\Nshe could fall under suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:13.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She had to put great effort into hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.54,0:17:16.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, she observed Okonogi-san's everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:25.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, she noticed that he was meeting\NTatematsu-san during his leisurely walk each day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:30.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ichikura san remembered having seen\NTatematsu-san's face somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because she had seen him on TV\Nas the most unlucky guy in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when Ichikura-san considered\Nusing Tatematsu-san in her plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:44.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, she followed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though she remembered his face from\NTV, she couldn't remember his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So to get his name...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan confirmed this with a resident of the same building.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:18:03.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She remembered a suspicious woman following\NTatematsu-san on his way back from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then put your plan to action.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:08.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, you stole something from Tatematsu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.97,0:18:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? You?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:18.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later that night, having discovered his name and address, you looked\Nup his phone number, called him, and threatened to silence him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:25.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You chose yesterday because you knew your fiancé,\NSakaki Kazuma-san, was attending a farewell party.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, he wouldn't be suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you put fake time bombs in the women's restroom\Non the 5th floor of the Touto Department Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, you quickly rushed to Beika District in order\Nto execute your murder plan on Tatematsu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, you tried to kill Okonogi-san while trying to make\NTatematsu-san's death seem like nothing more than collateral damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, you called the Touto Department Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:19:00.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've set time bombs up in the women's restroomon the 5th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:02.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Better hurry, before they explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:09.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the bombs revealed, you gauged the time for when\Nthere'd be a large commotion and typed out the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Ichikura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the truth of this fabricated alibi finally came to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a contradiction between the place where the\Nbombs actually were and what your message said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:28.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is conclusive proof of your evil deed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:44.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why was the position of the bombs changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:53.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that a child moved them while shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This world just isn't fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bombs changed position...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The old man who I thought would finally die didn't die...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And a famous detective appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I might be as unlucky as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you try to kill Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I thought about marrying you, I knew that\Nif the old man died, I'd get the inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't he quite healthy for an old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't wait for him to die naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Money?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:38.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of all things, that was your goal from the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:40.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:42.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without that, do you think you'd be anybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:50.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:51.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:53.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomomi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:20:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:01.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go call for a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's troubling you, Tomomi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad that you woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:44.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a horrible woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got the impression that she can still get a fresh start.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:51.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know it's a little bit strange coming\Nfrom an unlucky guy like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:55.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:21:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the only thing we can believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.84,0:23:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beer in the morning is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.26,0:23:40.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drinking it with coffee might be the perfect mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's the reason why...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:51.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's really an unlucky guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:58.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't laugh at others, you know.
